LanguageData.MaxStackLimitStat.Text:
Represents the adjusted maximum stack limit for {0}s on this this shelf. Calculated from
1. Normal StackLimit = {1}
2. Max Overstack Ratio = x{2}
3. Overstack Limit = (1) * (2) = {3}
4. MaxMassPerOverlaidThing = MaxStockWeight / OverlayLimit = {4}
5. MassStackLimit = MaxMassPerOverlaidThing / NormalThingMass = {5}
6. MaxStackLimit = Minimum(OverstackLimit, MassLimit) = {6}
